irst-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"3\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;font_color&quot;:&quot;#ffffff&quot;,&quot;content_alignment&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;title_color&quot;:&quot;#ffffff&quot;,&quot;headings_color&quot;:&quot;#ffffff&quot;}\" ><div style=\"text-align: left;\" data-title-color=\"#ffffff\" data-headings-color=\"#ffffff\" class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-398-3-0-0\" ><h3 class=\"widget-title\">The Secret Behind Your Success</h3><div class=\"textwidget\"><p>We are both remarkable at what we do.  So our goal is for you to keep creating content while we do the rest so we can both keep doing it all remarkably well.</p><p>Its quite simple you make content, we put it in front of the right peoples smiling faces, and we both reap the benefits.</p><p> </p><p>Here is one way to think about it:</p><p>Imagine your new Frankenstein cyborg creation is ready and its great, you are selling them to a few people out of your garage and you are getting by but you don\'t really have the time or even will to do anything but <strong>create</strong> and improve them.</p><p>That\'s where I come in.... so I build you a fancy store to sell them in and it all looks great, that\'s <strong>development.</strong></p><p>We talk some more and while you like the store you would like it more if people were actually in it....</p><p>So I create an event at The Festival which will demonstrate your Creation\'s cool abilities and I paint a sign saying ‘The Creation Demonstration coming to The Festival, Friday’, that’s <strong>advertising</strong>.</p><p>If you make an army of Scaled Down Abominable Creations and we walk them into town as they carry that sign, that’s <strong>promotion</strong>.</p><p>If the army gets hacked, starts taking over the world, and The Daily Show writes a story about it, that’s <strong>publicity</strong>.</p><p>And if I get the world to then laugh about it, that’s <strong>public relations</strong>.</p><p>If the town’s citizens go to see your creation, I show them the many ways it can entertain them, explain how much fun they’ll have spending money on one, answer their questions and ultimately, they buy a lot at the event, that’s <strong>sales</strong>.</p><p>And if I planned this whole thing, that’s <strong>marketing.</strong></p><p> </p><p>Chances are your situation is not quite as elaborate, but this is the secret to your success and what we do in a nutshell. The only difference is we do this all online, which is called <strong>web development and marketing</strong>.</p><p> </p><p> </p><p>So you want to take your business to the next level?  I\'ve been there!  It\'s not going to be easy, but we have the three phase plan that has worked for others in your situation.  Knowing you are headed in the right direction will make it easier.</p><p>First things first. We will assess your current marketing plan. Suggest tweaks or additions that</p><p>We can not wait to sit down and guide you through the process.</p><p> </p><p> </p><p>In this section your in total agreement with them. You agree that everyones marketing needs are different, they can\'t follow a cookie cutter plan. Also, you agree that they need to free their mind and continue what they do best which is making content. Also, they need to do content marketing. Also, they need to look presentable. Unfortuantely if their m ind is free to creat content that means they really cant be doing the other things.</p><p> </p><p>]</p><p>Content advertising</p><p> </p><p>A custom plan to target your audience usingn what ever stream of information they trust.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-398-4\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-has-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;row_stretch&quot;:&quot;full&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;,&quot;align&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;overlay&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;overlay_color&quot;:&quot;#000000&quot;}\" ><div c