ore that plan even goes into motion something even more powerful graces it with its energies...</p><p>Get this!  When you send in your Expansion Idea it gets uploaded to a flash drive in Tibet where a monastery full of the most spiritual monks meditate to check basic viability of that idea in this market.  Chakras are performed.  Auras can flare. And if the idea marinades in Earth\'s ether just right and with enough energy to compel a white dove to soar from Tibet to New York whilst carrying that flash drive, then the idea was meant to be.  Suggested tweaks or additions will come in the form of intuition which we will communicate to you upon visiting for tea. Namaste.</p><p> </p><p>But enough about the initial process. What happens after that?</p><p> </p><p>Well, here is one way to think about the happenings:</p><p>Imagine your new Frankenstein Cyborg Baby <strong>creation</strong> is ready and it is just great.  You just know that they are gonna be the newest and coolest, and totally replace robot butlers forever.  But you are stuck selling them to a few people out of your garage which doesn\'t work well and brings you away from the fun part, like coming up with a better design for its fully reticulating neck and programming it to collect cobwebs off the ceiling.</p><p>That\'s where I come in.... so I build you a fancy store to sell them in making it all look very professional. Well call that <strong>development.</strong></p><p>We talk some more and while you like the store you would like it more if people were actually going into it....</p><p>So here is where it gets interesting.  I plan an event at The Festival which will demonstrate your Creation\'s cool abilities and I paint a sign saying ‘The Creation Demonstration coming to The Festival, Friday’, that’s <strong>advertising</strong>.</p><p>If you make an army of Scaled Down Abominable Creations and we walk them into town as they carry that sign, that’s <strong>promotion</strong>.</p><p>If the army gets hacked, starts taking over the world, and The Daily Show writes a story about it, that’s <strong>publicity</strong>.</p><p>And if I get the world to then laugh about it, that’s <strong>public relations</strong>.</p><p>If the town’s citizens go to see your creation, I show them the many ways it can entertain and make them happier, explain how much fun they’ll have spending money on one, answer their questions and ultimately, they buy a lot at the event, that’s <strong>sales</strong>.</p><p>And if I planned this entire thing, that’s <strong>marketing.</strong></p><p> </p><p><strong>This is the secret to your success</strong> and what we do in a nutshell!!  The only difference is we do this all online, so it is called <strong>WEB development and marketing.</strong></p><p>So there is the secret!</p><p> </p><p> </p><p>Also, the universe is telling me that by getting our <strong>monthly newsletter</strong> you will become fully enlightened and reach nirvana... as long as your nirvana is growing your business. Namaste.</p><p> </p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-439-4\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-has-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;row_stretch&quot;:&quot;full&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;,&quot;align&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;overlay&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;overlay_color&quot;:&quot;#000000&quot;}\" ><div class=\"siteorigin-panels-stretch panel-row-style panel-row-style-for-439-4\" style=\"padding: 100px 0; \" data-stretch-type=\"full\" data-overlay=\"true\" data-overlay-color=\"#000000\" ><div id=\"pgc-439-4-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"1\" ><div id=\"panel-439-4-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child panel-last-child\" data-index=\"4\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;content_alignment&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;title_color&quot;:&quot;#777777&quot;,&quot;headings_color&quot;:&quot;#777777&quot;}\" ><div style=\"text-align: left;\" data-title-color=\"#777777\" data-headings-color=\"#777777\" class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-439-4-0-0\" ><h3 class=\"widget-title\">Most Recent Articles on Web Development and Marketing</h3><div class=\"textwidget\"><p>Front end development</p><p> </p><p>Content advertising</p><p>A custom plan to target your audience usingn what ever stream of information they trust.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div><div id=\"pg-439-5\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-has-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;row_stretch&quot;:&quot;full&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;,&quot;align&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;background_image&quot;:&quot;275&quot;,&quot;overlay&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;overlay_color&quot;:&quot;#000000&quot;}\" ><div class=\"siteorigin-panels-stretch panel-row-style panel-row-style-for-439-5\" style=\"background-image: url(http://www.localhost/fco/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/bigstock-Zen-Stones-Balance-81353279-Copy.jpg);padding: 100px 0; \" data-stretch-type=\"full\" data-hasbg=\"hasbg\" data-overlay=\"true\" data-overlay-color=\"#000000\" ><div id=\"pgc-439-5-0\"  class=\"panel-grid-cell\"  data-weight=\"1\" ><div id=\"panel-439-5-0-0\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_black-studio-tinymce widget_black_studio_tinymce panel-first-child\" data-index=\"5\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_image_attachment&quot;:false,&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;font_color&quot;:&quot;#ffffff&quot;,&quot;content_alignment&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;title_color&quot;:&quot;#ffffff&quot;,&quot;headings_color&quot;:&quot;#ffffff&quot;}\" ><div style=\"text-align: left;\" data-title-color=\"#ffffff\" data-headings-color=\"#ffffff\" class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-439-5-0-0\" ><h3 class=\"widget-title\">&#8220;We Believe the Best Company Should Win&#8221;</h3><div class=\"textwidget\"><h3>If you are ready to take on more clientele, then it is time for you to get an affordable professionally created and managed online presence and trust me, we are the team to do that.</h3><h3>Why us?  What makes us special?  Well, we are a team of maverick free-lancers who are familiar with working together. We are able to tailor every man hour.  Since it is such a modular work environment this means you are never paying money for something you do not need.  </h3><h3>Need a fully loaded website in a month? Even after you vet them A free lancer or two would burn out trying to do that.  I wonder how the product would look?  I wonder how clean it would be under the hood?  I wonder what would happen to your asset if one or both of those freelancers moved, would you still get post project support for your asset? Anyway, among freelancers we are the most affordable because jobs aren\'t as unreliable. And don\'t even get me started with a corporation on this project unless you want to be paying for the entire scrum management team and their pensions. Talk about overhead. Not to mention they might treat you like a number.  They might wonder why you are coming to them with such a dinky project.</h3><h3>You get the benefits of hiring a large businesses as well as all of the benefits of hiring a freelancer,  with none of the negatives.   We have a name to uphold its called accountability</h3><h3>So this is what really sets us apart.  Why isn\'t anyone else doing this? Putting together a team of free lancers.  Well, collaboration has never been so easy.  Flower City Online has created a seamless workflow, making it possible for us if we wanted to have 14 people on a job each putting in an hour a day and sending it to the master.</h3><h3>Again, we promise we won\'t quote you a price unless it is a win-win for both of us.  Our goal is to earn your business for the long term.  So send us your thoughts today if you think we can work together to grow your business.</h3><h3> </h3><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p><h3>You don\'t see many of these teams because corporations are safe and cushy and offer many benefits and would steal freelancers away too quickly... but this is changing.  Even some of our developers are working full time and contribute when they can, but that is a busy life style with a family.  No, but most of our developers have been working for us since they first became what the corporate world would call junior developers.  Because of this experience they know so much more than software development.  Going to the 9-5 and just coding would get boring.  We sacrifice full time benefits though.  Our loss your gain.</h3><p> </p></div></div></div><div id=\"panel-439-5-0-1\" class=\"so-panel widget widget_siteorigin-panels-builder panel-last-child\" data-index=\"6\" data-style=\"{&quot;background_display&quot;:&quot;tile&quot;,&quot;content_alignment&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;title_color&quot;:&quot;#ffffff&quot;,&quot;headings_color&quot;:&quot;#ffffff&quot;}\" ><div style=\"text-align: left;\" data-title-color=\"#ffffff\" data-headings-color=\"#ffffff\" class=\"panel-widget-style panel-widget-style-for-439-5-0-1\" ><div id=\"pl-w5983878a83139\"  class=\"panel-layout\" ><div id=\"pg-w5983878a83139-0\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-has-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;cell_class&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;row_css&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;mobile_css&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;padding&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;bottom_margin&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;gutter&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;row_stretch&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;collapse_behaviour&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;collapse_order&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;,&quot;mobile_padding&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;bottom_border&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;background&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;color&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;background_image&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;overlay_color&quot;:&quot;#000000&quot;}\" ><div style=\"padding: 100px 0; \" data-overlay=\"true\" data-overlay-color=\"#000000\" class=\"panel-row-style panel-row-style-for-w5983878a83139-0