ent creators are intamitely familiar with thei r characteristics their passion triggers and the direction you wan tthem to take. The DOA is also responsible for building assets like direct mail lists, direct email lists, and encryptions that can grow and be segmented as your content missions grows and expands.</p>\n<p>The channel master, wherever your content is headed social media, email, print, end user, the  CM is  responsible for getting the most and what works best on each channel. What works best on SlideShare? When should you send your reminder email newsletters and how frequently? Whats the proper ratio of owned versus curated content your business should distribute on twitter? Whos keeping track of mobile strategy and execution? Youchannel will look to this guy for answers.</p>\n<p>The Chief Technologist, as marketing information technology continues to merge there will be a need of at least one individual whos sole purpose is to leverage the proper use of these technologies into the content marketing process the person will be responsable for your publishing systems or the plumbing such as your website infrastructure and email systems and how they integrate together.</p>\n<p>The creative director, the desiugn and creative look to your content is more important thatn ever especially as creative and social channels become an increasingly important method of attracting and maintaining subscribers. The CD is responsible for the overall look and fell of all your content including your website your blog, images, photography, and every other piece of collateral you create.</p>\n<p>Influencer relations, the role formerly known as media relations will evolve into that a manager of influencers, this persons responsibilities include developing your hit list of influencers, maintaining your direct relationships with them, and integrating them into your marketing process in the most impactful ways. Freelancer and agency relations, as content demands continue to evolve and increase, your orgs relations with freelancers and other content venders will grow as well. The orgs need to cultivate their own expert teams and network and it is this persons job to negotiate rates and responsibilities are united in their work on behalf of your Content Inc. program.</p>\n<p>The Content curation director, as you begin to develop content assets you will have amazing opportunities to repackage and repurpose your content. But the role of the content manager is to look at all the assets being developed by the organization and strategize ways to create new pieces of content form them. This involves taking other people’s content, adding to it, enhancing it, and/or giving it a new context or perspective so that it evolves into a new piece of content. They are responsible for understanding the content assets available to work with including text image audio, effectively tagging, categorizing, and coordinating these materials into a data asset management system, working with the content marketing team on a clear channel plan, and developing and managing content marketing plan, developing and executing strategy by using existing resources.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<p> </p>\n<div id=\"pg-3543-1\" class=\"panel-grid ppb-row\">\n<div class=\"ppb-row panel-row-style panel-row-style- ppb-stretch-full-width\">\n<div class=\"panel-grid-cell-container\">\n<div id=\"pgc-3543-1-1\" class=\"ppb-col panel-grid-cell \">\n<div id=\"panel-3543-1-1-0\" class=\"ppb-block\">\n<h2>Kevin Jones, The Founder</h2>\n<p>When I was young, I watched in awe as my father took an old MG sports car down to its frame, and then rebuilt the whole thing. I was hooked! I inherited his fascination for breaking things into their component parts. I love to figure out how things work, and then improve on the model to make it work better. And that’s exactly what I do at Ectobox.</p>\n<p>Meanwhile, my professional background in Accounting keeps me grounded. I know that at the end of the day, the numbers have to add up. To grow your business you need more money coming in than going out. Your time, your people’s time, and your systems are all valuable resources your control. No matter how strong your company’s revenues are, if you’re bleeding money from these areas, it’s a drag on profits. I’m passionate about building, and my favorite thing to do is build businesses. Just like you, I work hard to make sure my own company is efficient in our processes and our systems, so I can keep my overhead low. And I personally oversee every project to make sure the job gets done right. Like you, I don’t like to waste money. I like to get things done. Just ask our <a title=\"Clients\" href=\"http://www.ectobox.com/clients/\">clients</a>.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"pg-3543-2\" class=\"panel-grid ppb-row\">\n<div class=\"ppb-row panel-row-style panel-row-style- ppb-stretch-full-width\">\n<div class=\"panel-grid-cell-container\">\n<div id=\"pgc-3543-2-0\" class=\"ppb-col panel-grid-cell \"> </div>\n<div id=\"pgc-3543-2-1\" class=\"ppb-col panel-grid-cell \">\n<div id=\"panel-3543-2-1-0\" class=\"ppb-block\">\n<h2>OUR PROCESS</h2>\n</div>\n<div id=\"panel-3543-2-1-1\" class=\"ppb-block ppb-no-mobile-spacing\">\n<p>We take the builder\'s approach of \"measure twice, cut once\". That\'s how carpenters avoid costly mistakes, and it makes the same good sense in the world of custom software design.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"pg-3543-4\" class=\"panel-grid ppb-row\">\n<div class=\"ppb-row panel-row-style panel-row-style- ppb-stretch-full-width\">\n<div class=\"panel-grid-cell-container\">\n<div id=\"pgc-3543-4-0\" class=\"ppb-col panel-grid-cell \">\n<div id=\"panel-3543-4-0-0\" class=\"ppb-block\">\n<h2>OUR VALUES</h2>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"pg-3543-5\" class=\"panel-grid ppb-row\">\n<div class=\"ppb-row panel-row-style panel-row-style- ppb-stretch-full-width\">\n<div class=\"panel-grid-cell-container\">\n<div id=\"pgc-3543-5-0\" class=\"ppb-col panel-grid-cell \"> </div>\n<div id=\"pgc-3543-5-1\" class=\"ppb-col panel-grid-cell \">\n<div id=\"panel-3543-5-1-0\" class=\"ppb-block infobox_about\">\n<h2>WE ARE HONEST</h2>\n<div class=\"woo-sc-hr\"> </div>\n<ul>\n<li>We don’t sell what you don’t need.</li>\n<li>We won\'t lie to you.</li>\n<li>We guarantee a fit between the project and the team or we won\'t accept the work.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div id=\"panel-3543-5-1-1\" class=\"ppb-block infobox_about\">\n<h2>WE ARE DEPENDABLE</h2>\n<div class=\"woo-sc-hr\"> </div>\n<ul>\n<li>We\'ll be there.</li>\n<li>We won\'t flake out on you.</li>\n<li>We will be available.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"pgc-3543-5-2\" class=\"ppb-col panel-grid-cell \">\n<div id=\"panel-3543-5-2-0\" class=\"ppb-block infobox_about\">\n<h2>WE WORK SMART</h2>\n<div class=\"woo-sc-hr\"> </div>\n<ul>\n<li>We define the real problem.</li>\n<li>We do the right work or we don’t do it at all.</li>\n<li>We believe in efficiency, no wasted time, money, or effort.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div id=\"panel-3543-5-2-1\" class=\"ppb-block infobox_about\">\n<h2>WE COMMUNICATE</h2>\n<div class=\"woo-sc-hr\"> </div>\n<ul>\n<li>From sales to service to follow up, we answer the phone. We provide premium custom software design, development, and service to meet your needs.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n</div></div></div></div></div></div></div>','About Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','171-revision-v1','','','2017-08-05 06:09:20','2017-08-05 06:09:20','',171,'http://www.localhost/fco/171-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(470,1,'2017-08-05 06:13:58','2017-08-05 06:13:58','<div id=\"pl-89\"  class=\"panel-layout\" ><div id=\"pg-89-0\"  class=\"panel-grid panel-has-style\"  data-style=\"{&quot;row_stretch&quot;:&quot;full&quot;,&quot;cell_alignment&quot;:&quot;flex-start&quot;,&quot;align&quot;:&quot;&quot