rking simultaneously in wordpress with someone other than myself.  It wont be crucial if they are just changing the javascript things though. Since this is easy, compressable, and now its installed I might choose this. option.\r\n\r\nI have also been tryign different file types to see if github is able to parse and make them versionable.... may have found the one. I saved the DB as CodeGen and a .cs file came out that looks incredibly promising. Turns out github was not able to detect the content changes.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nNOw there are these two compeeting (https://stackoverflow.com/questions/37385823/liquibase-vs-flyway-which-one-to-use) db migration tools: flyway(https://flywaydb.org/getstarted/download) and Liquibase(http://download.liquibase.org/)','CMS WordPress DB Versioning and Syncing With GitHub: A \'how to\' on Continuous Deployment','','inherit','closed','closed','','498-revision-v1','','','2017-08-08 06:17:10','2017-08-08 06:17:10','',498,'http://www.localhost/fco/498-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(513,1,'2017-08-08 06:20:03','2017-08-08 06:20:03','Not well  documented but I think i have figured it out.... Only stack exchange offered manual answers, and there was a wp plugin. All other solutions are expensive as hell.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nobviously in 2010 it was still an issue\r\n\r\nfound this round about way on the way bottom of the discussion\r\n\r\nhttps://stackoverflow.com/questions/846659/how-can-i-put-a-database-under-git-version-control/28123546#28123546\r\n\r\ncool video though\r\n\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c45AevIuYGk\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nin 2012 there was an answer, and one Im considering\r\n<h3 class=\"r\"><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/questions/13608706/using-version-control-git-on-a-mysql-database\">Using version control (Git) on a MySQL database - Stack Overflow</a></h3>\r\nhttps://stackoverflow.com/questions/13608706/using-version-control-git-on-a-mysql-database\r\n\r\nQ:\r\n\r\nI am a WordPress Design